				<td colspan='2' class='diff-ntitle'><div id="mw-diff-ntitle1"><strong><a href="/w/index.php?title=Pierre_Trudeau&amp;oldid=638504227" title="Pierre Trudeau">Revision as of 15:44, 17 December 2014</a> <span class="mw-diff-edit">(<a href="/w/index.php?title=Pierre_Trudeau&amp;action=edit&amp;oldid=638504227" title="Pierre Trudeau">edit</a>)</span> <span class="mw-diff-undo">(<a href="/w/index.php?title=Pierre_Trudeau&amp;action=edit&amp;undoafter=638114854&amp;undo=638504227" title="&quot;Undo&quot; reverts this edit and opens the edit form in preview mode. It allows adding a reason in the summary.">undo</a>)</span></strong></div><div id="mw-diff-ntitle2"><a href="/wiki/Special:Contributions/198.103.249.251" title="Special:Contributions/198.103.249.251" class="mw-userlink mw-anonuserlink">198.103.249.251</a> <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/wiki/User_talk:198.103.249.251" title="User talk:198.103.249.251">talk</a>)</span> </div><div id="mw-diff-ntitle3"> <span class="comment">(<a href="#Prime_Minister.2C_1974-79">→</a>‎<span dir="auto"><span class="autocomment">Prime Minister, 1974-79</span></span>)</span></div><div id="mw-diff-ntitle5"></div><div id="mw-diff-ntitle4"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Pierre_Trudeau&amp;diff=next&amp;oldid=638504227" title="Pierre Trudeau" id="differences-nextlink">Next edit →</a></div></td>
