  <td class="diff-marker">&#160;</td>
  <td class="diff-context"><div>As the PQ began to take power, Trudeau faced the prolonged failure of his marriage, which was covered in lurid detail on a day-by-day basis by the English language press.  Trudeau's reserve was seen as dignified by contemporaries and his poll numbers actually rose during the height of coverage,{{sfn|English (2009)|p=329}} but aides felt the personal tensions left him uncharacteristically emotional and prone to outbursts. {{sfn|English (2009)|p=327-8}}</div></td>
  <td class="diff-marker">&#160;</td>
  <td class="diff-context"><div>As the PQ began to take power, Trudeau faced the prolonged failure of his marriage, which was covered in lurid detail on a day-by-day basis by the English language press.  Trudeau's reserve was seen as dignified by contemporaries and his poll numbers actually rose during the height of coverage,{{sfn|English (2009)|p=329}} but aides felt the personal tensions left him uncharacteristically emotional and prone to outbursts. {{sfn|English (2009)|p=327-8}}</div></td>
</tr>
