<li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Pierre_Trudeau&amp;action=edit"><span title="Edit this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;">e</span></a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div style="font-size:110%"><strong class="selflink">Pierre Trudeau</strong></div>
</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td colspan="2"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-abovebelow" colspan="2">
<div>
<ul>
<li>October 18, 1919 – September 28, 2000<br />
<a href="/wiki/Prime_Minister_of_Canada" title="Prime Minister of Canada">Prime Minister of Canada</a> (1968–1979, 1980-1984)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Liberal_Party_of_Canada" title="Liberal Party of Canada">Leader of the Liberal Party of Canada</a> (1968-1984)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Member_of_Parliament" title="Member of Parliament" class="mw-redirect">Member of Parliament</a> for <a href="/wiki/Mount_Royal_(electoral_district)" title="Mount Royal (electoral district)">Mount Royal</a> (1965–1984)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Leader_of_the_Official_Opposition_(Canada)" title="Leader of the Official Opposition (Canada)">Leader of the Opposition</a> (1979-1980)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
